I be await the sunrise gaze modestly through the cold morning once it come you lie embrace us over Autumn 's proud treetop I stand motionless in a parade of fall rain your voice I can hear as I be fall again devotion elude and in sadness I lumber in my own ash I be stand without a soul she weep and whisper : " I know ... " we walk into the night be I to bid you farewell ? why ca n't you see that I try ? when every tear I shed be for you ? _________________________ name to Bid You farewell Artist Opeth album Morningrise